msgstr "`@ProjectedFieldName` 注解还支持 HQL 表达式，包括聚合函数。这对 GROUP BY 查询特别有用："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In case you want to project an entity in a class with nested classes, you can use the `@NestedProjectedClass` annotation on those nested classes."
msgstr "如果你想在包含嵌套类的类中投影一个实体，可以在这些嵌套类上使用 `@NestedProjectedClass` 注解。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
