msgstr "当您需要将 `@Embedded` 实体或 `@ManyToOne` 、 `@OneToOne` 关系进行投影时，可以使用此注解。它不支持 `@OneToMany` 或 `@ManyToMany` 关系。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It is also possible to specify a HQL query with a select clause. In this case, the projection class must have a constructor\n"
