#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Add this dependency to your `pom.xml`:"
msgstr "将此依赖项添加到你的 `pom.xml` 中："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Given this simple entity:"
msgstr "假设有一个这样的简单实体："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
